                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890422-39-off167 t17890422-39-cd168"></join>, a flock-bed, value 2 s. a featherbed, value 10 s. a bolster, value 2 s. a pair of sheets, value 3 s. a linen sheet, value 1 s. a pair of bellows, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17890422-39-victim362" type="victimName">
